{
  "page": "Wayfarer's Rest",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Wayfarer's Rest</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">House Vance of Wayfarer's Rest</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> probably located in the western part of the region near the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> and the border with the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Location_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Location-2\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a> and her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Dreamfyre\" title=\"Dreamfyre\">Dreamfyre</a>, briefly stayed with the Vances of Wayfarer's Rest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Karyl_Vance\" title=\"Karyl Vance\">Karyl Vance</a> becomes Lord of Wayfarer's Rest after the death of his father in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth\">battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Oxcross\" title=\"Battle of Oxcross\">Battle of Oxcross</a>, captives such as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lymond_Vikary\" title=\"Lymond Vikary\">Lymond Vikary</a> are held here.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Wayfarer's Rest is a reference by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> to Liane the Wayfarer from <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Dying_Earth\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The Dying Earth\">The Dying Earth</a></i> by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Vance\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Jack Vance\">Jack Vance</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Location-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Location_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">During the early stage of both the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a> the riverlands was invaded by a <a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">westermen</a> host. A rivermen host composed of men sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">House Piper</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Pinkmaiden_Castle\" title=\"Pinkmaiden Castle\">Pinkmaiden Castle</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">House Vance</a> of Wayfarer's Rest, was hastly gathered on both occasion to repel the invasions. Given that Pinkmaiden's location is known to be on the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> near the border with the westerlands, everything suggests Wayfarer's Rest is also located in this general area of the riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wayfarer%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Appendix\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, A Time of Testing - The Realm Remade.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_71\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 71\">Chapter 71</a>, Catelyn XI.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><t